      <title>规模达 3500 亿美元的基金将受到标普新指数上限规则的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/funds-with-350-billion-are-exposed-to-s-p-s-new-index-cap-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔道琼斯指数公司修改了规则，以遏制大公司的主导地位。本月晚些时候，资产规模达 3500 亿美元的指数跟踪股票基金将进行大规模改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/funds-with-350-billion-are-exposed-to-s-p-s-new-index-cap-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 14:06:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
