      <title>贝莱德的里德：市场降息定价“激进”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-06/blackrock-s-rieder-market-rate-cut-pricing-aggressive-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德全球固定收益首席投资官里克·里德 (Rick Rieder) 认为，美联储应该在本月晚些时候降息 50 个基点，但他预计美联储将“谨慎”降息 25 个基点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-06/blackrock-s-rieder-market-rate-cut-pricing-aggressive-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 13:53:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲警告俄罗斯天然气被秘密混入供应中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/europe-warned-about-russian-gas-being-secretly-mixed-into-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位有望负责欧盟能源政策的候选人表示，欧盟明年的天然气供应中可能暗中混入来自俄罗斯的天然气，当现行过境协议到期时，这将给莫斯科带来一个不理想的解决办法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/europe-warned-about-russian-gas-being-secretly-mixed-into-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 13:48:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储威廉姆斯：现在适合降低利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-06/fed-s-williams-says-it-is-now-appropriate-to-reduce-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约联邦储备银行行长约翰·威廉姆斯表示，现在央行降息是适当的，因为美联储在实现维持物价稳定和充分就业的双重目标方面取得了“重大进展”。威廉姆斯周五在一次演讲中表示：“随着经济目前处于平衡状态，通胀率有望达到 2%，现在通过降低联邦基金利率目标区间来降低政策立场的限制程度是适当的。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-06/fed-s-williams-says-it-is-now-appropriate-to-reduce-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 13:24:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储威廉姆斯称现在适合降低利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/fed-s-williams-says-now-appropriate-to-lower-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约联邦储备银行行长约翰威廉姆斯表示，鉴于降低通胀和劳动力市场降温的进展，现在央行降低利率是适当的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/fed-s-williams-says-now-appropriate-to-lower-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 12:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
